data.description: Beautiful home located on a shady lot with no thru-traffic! Located in a historical district, this home offers a large living area with wood floors on the main level along with a den, kitchen, two bedrooms and two baths.  New flooring in main bedroom and den. New stovetop and venthood in kitchen. Downstairs is a bedroom, bathroom, dining area and another large living area which could be a gameroom or bonus room.  Step outside to the privacy of your own pool and spa.  See Private Remarks.
